init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The movie is a documentary of your next life, and you watch it as it unfolds.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are bored out of your mind, and you can't wait for the movie to be over.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "So, what do you think of the movie?" you ask him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "What was that one about?" you ask.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Well, it was about a guy who was born in a small town in the middle of nowhere, and he lived a very boring life

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Yeah, but this guy was a total loser.
